3:04:57 +0000","published_by":1},{"id":22,"title":"如何在Openshift上安装FFMPEG","slug":"%e5%a6%82%e4%bd%95%e5%9c%a8openshift%e4%b8%8a%e5%ae%89%e8%a3%85ffmpeg","markdown":"\n因为里区要推出在线看片功能..所以研究了一下\n\n首先,你需要安装rhc(这个大家应该都安装了吧\n\n然后打开Git bash,键入以下指令(先rhc ssh\n\n```\ncd $OPENSHIFT_DATA_DIR\nmkdir bin\nwget http://www.tortall.net/projects/yasm/releases/yasm-1.2.0.tar.gz\nwget http://ffmpeg.org/releases/ffmpeg-2.0.1.tar.gz\n\ntar -xvf yasm-1.2.0.tar.gz\ncd yasm-1.2.0\n./configure --prefix=$OPENSHIFT_DATA_DIR/bin --bindir=$OPENSHIFT_DATA_DIR/bin\nmake\nmake install\nexport PATH=$OPENSHIFT_DATA_DIR/bin:$PATH\n \ncd $OPENSHIFT_DATA_DIR\ntar -xvf ffmpeg-2.0.1.tar.gz\ncd ffmpeg-2.0.1\n./configure --prefix=$OPENSHIFT_DATA_DIR/bin --bindir=$OPENSHIFT_DATA_DIR/bin\nmake\nmake install\n```\n\n换新版本的话只要替换url即可,另外一定到准备好空间,不然分分钟玩脱\n\n\n","html":"<p>因为里区要推出在线看片功能..所以研究了一下</p>\n<p>首先,你需要安装rhc(这个大家应该都安装了吧</p>\n<p>然后打开Git bash,键入以下指令(先rhc ssh</p>\n<pre><code>cd $OPENSHIFT_DATA_DIR\nmkdir bin\nwget http://www.tortall.net/projects/yasm/releases/yasm-1.2.0.tar.gz\nwget http://ffmpeg.org/releases/ffmpeg-2.0.1.tar.gz\n\ntar -xvf yasm-1.2.0.tar.gz\ncd yasm-1.2.0\n./configure --prefix=$OPENSHIFT_DATA_DIR/bin --bindir=$OPENSHIFT_DATA_DIR/bin\nmake\nmake install\nexport PATH=$OPENSHIFT_DATA_DIR/bin:$PATH\n \ncd $OPENSHIFT_DATA_DIR\ntar -xvf ffmpeg-2.0.1.tar.gz\ncd ffmpeg-2.0.1\n./configure --prefix=$OPENSHIFT_DATA_DIR/bin --bindir=$OPENSHIFT_DATA_DIR/bin\nmake\nmake install\n</code></pre>\n<p>换新版本的话只要替换url即可,另外一定到准备好空间,不然分分钟玩脱</p>\n","image":null,"featured":0,"page":0,"status":"published","language":"en_US","meta_title":null,"meta_description":null,"author_id":1,"created_at":"Wed, 29 Oct 2014 21:17:43 +0000","created_by":1,"updated_at":"Wed, 04 May 2016 23:15:53 +0000","updated_by":1,"published_at":"Wed, 29 Oct 2014 21:17:43 +0000","published_by":1},{"id":25,"title":"Takethislollipop,一个不错的小游戏","slug":"takethislollipop%e4%b8%80%e4%b8%aa%e4%b8%8d%e9%94%99%e7%9a%84%e5%b0%8f%e6%b8%b8%e6%88%8f","markdown":"\n